t the signs of resilience in the domestic \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2  would continue in the fourth quarter of 2023, thanks to the manufacturing purchasing managers' index (\uc2 PMI\uc2 ), which is consistently in the expansionary zone at over 50 percent and the trade balance surplus.\par \par \uc2 RIANI SANUSI PUTRI\par \par \uc2 Editor's Choice: How to Get Singapore Citizenship for Indonesians\par \par \uc2 Click here to get the latest news updates from Tempo on Google News\par \par {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://statik.tempo.co/data/2024/01/29/id_1275603/1275603_720.jpg"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 Click here to view picture}}}\par \par \uc2 Document TEMPOE0020240130ek1u0008f\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw139\pich40\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal2085\pichgoal600
