ly support the IKN to be completed soon," he added.\par \par \uc2 Meanwhile, House member Arsyadjuliandi Rahman urged the OIKN to be more active in sharing information about legal certainty regarding investment in Nusantara.\par \par \uc2 He revealed that there is doubt from the private sector, especially regarding land issues and legal certainties.\par \par \uc2 "These regional entrepreneurs want to get information on how they can participate in \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  development in Nusantara," he said.\par \par \uc2 (T.KR-KZU/B/T008/T008) 18-03-2024 22:33:21\par \par \uc2 Document ANTARA0020240318ek3i001e2\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw177\pich40\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal2655\pichgoal600
